&lt;p&gt;기본적으로 Borderless 테마에서 프로필 아래 아이콘이 5개가 있었습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;대부분이 잘 알고있는 &lt;strong&gt;Facebook , Instagram , Github&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
저한테는 조금 생소했던 &lt;strong&gt;Linkedin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;위 4가지 아이콘은 원하는대로 보이고 안보이고를 정할 수 있었습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 503px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/static/a59a76f85a725355e2543c58081214fd/a4078/Config.png&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 43.91891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;Config&quot;
        title=&quot;Config&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/a59a76f85a725355e2543c58081214fd/a4078/Config.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/a59a76f85a725355e2543c58081214fd/12f09/Config.png 148w,
/static/a59a76f85a725355e2543c58081214fd/e4a3f/Config.png 295w,
/static/a59a76f85a725355e2543c58081214fd/a4078/Config.png 503w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 503px) 100vw, 503px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&apos; &apos; 와 같이 공백으로 처리하면 자동으로 아이콘이 사라집니다..!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;그런데 아이콘 하나가 계속해서 사라졌습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;바로 &lt;strong&gt;RSS 아이콘.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 104px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/static/60bcdb87264fa96dd9cdc060ada27db6/c6fc0/RSS.png&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 31.730769230769234%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
